urrency account <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nmicrochip implant:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA Military-Funded Biosensor Could Be the Future of Pandemic Detection<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.defenseone.com/technology/2020/03/military-funded-biosensor-could-be-future-pandemic-detection/163497/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defenseone.com%2Ftechnology%2F2020%2F03%2Fmilitary-funded-biosensor-could-be-future-pandemic-detection%2F163497%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=6a62e9e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.defenseone.com/technology/2020/03/military-funded-biosensor-could-be-future-pandemic-detection/163497/</a><br />\nWhy are pandemics so hard to stop? Often it&rsquo;s because the disease moves faster than people can be tested for it. The Defense Department is helping to fund a new study to determine whether an under-the-skin biosensor can help trackers keep up &mdash; by detecting flu-like infections even before their symptoms begin to show. Its maker, Profusa, says the sensor is on track to try for FDA approval by early next year.<br />\n<br />\nThe sensor has two parts. One is a 3mm string of hydrogel, a material whose network of polymer chains is used in some contact lenses and other implants. Inserted under the skin with a syringe, the string includes a specially engineered molecule that sends a fluorescent signal outside of the body when the body begins to fight an infection. The other part is an electronic component attached to the skin. It sends light through the skin, detects the fluorescent signal and generates another signal that the wearer can send to a doctor, website, etc. It&rsquo;s like a blood lab on the skin that can pick up the body&rsquo;s response to illness before the presence of other symptoms, like coughing.<br />\n<br />\nPentagon 個合約比咗中國人話事嘅公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n3bNb9qFiMg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn3bNb9qFiMg&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=fdfced87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n3bNb9qFiMg</a><br />\n<br />\n想取消social distancing, 就要 contact tracing + mandatory vaccination<br />\ncontact tracing + mandatory vaccination = microchip implant <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nhydrogel研究都係中國人係MIT帶嘅project <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KjpPnOy6cBQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKjpPnOy6cBQ&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=c024beee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KjpPnOy6cBQ</a>"},{"pid":"3a0ddf4fb8138d69a13831888246168358dd2d20","tid":2283663,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T18:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}